<HEADLINE> UNSCOM Executive Chairman to Visit Britain </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
UNITED NATIONS, April 1 (Xinhua) -- Richard Butler, executive
chairman of the United Nations Special Commission (UNSCOM) in
charge of dismantling Iraq's weapons of mass destruction, will
visit London from April 2 to 3, the U.N. spokesman's office
announced Wednesday.
