<HEADLINE> Shanghai Stock Index Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 2 (Xinhua) -- The Composite Stock Index on the
Shanghai Stock Exchange finished at 1,269.01 today, up 14.05
points from the previous session, according to the Guangfa
Securities Co. Ltd.
</P>
<P>
The SSR-30 index, based on 30 blue chips that are selected from
more than 200 A shares for domestic investors on the Shanghai
Stock Exchange, closed at 3,803.52, up 41.80 points from the
previous session.
</P>
