close political and economic ties, can further cooperate with each
other and with the region, especially in addressing the current
economic turmoil, Peterson said.
</P>
<P>
Peterson, who also discussed the haze problem with Anwar,
expressed Canada's willingness to extend its technical expertise
in combating forest fires and the haze problem to Malaysia.
</P>
<P>
"Canada has the knowledge and expertise in this area and we are
willing to send water bombers if there is a need and request from
Malaysia," Peterson said, adding that no such request had been
made so far. 
