trade deficit is to have a large volume of trade as it diminishes
the deficit."
</P>
<P>
On the establishment of a "Partnership Committee" between the
two countries, which was also discussed by the Turkish foreign
minister and Pakistani leaders, Cem said the two sides have
started substantive work on a substantial timetable with organized
mechanism so that the bilateral relationship can develop in a more
organized framework.
</P>
<P>
"This is to place our relationship within a framework which has
a mechanism of further development," he said.
