<HEADLINE> Zambia Bans Fruitless Workshops </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LUSAKA, April 2 (Xinhua) -- Zambian new Health Minister Nkandu
Luo has banned fruitless workshops, Zambia Daily Mail reported
Thursday.
