<DATE_TIME> 1998-04-02 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Thai Bourse Index Down 2.69 Points </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, April 2 (Xinhua) -- The Stock Exchange of Thailand
