<HEADLINE> East China Talent Market for Elderly Citizens </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
FUZHOU, April 2 (Xinhua) -- A talent market in Quanzhou, Fujian
Province, has supplied over 10,000 retired professionals for local
economic sectors nationwide.
</P>
<P>
The market has sponsored over a dozen talent exchange fairs for
elderly citizens in recent years. Numerous elderly professionals
have found new jobs following retirement, with enterprise managers
warmly welcoming their rich working experience.
</P>
<P>
Statistics show that more than 100,000 retirees in the province
have found new jobs with some 5,000 enterprises over the past five
years. 
</P>
</TEXT>
